<p>
If you want to use the Gambit Scheme compiler, <code>gsc</code>, to
compile Scheme files you will need the <code>gcc</code> C compiler.
The easiest way to get <code>gcc</code> is to install Apple's Xcode
Developer Tools.  The Xcode installer is distributed on the MacOS
install DVDs and can also be downloaded from Apple Developper
Connection
<a href="http://developer.apple.com/tools/download/">Xcode download page</a>.
</p>

<p>
Gambit can be uninstalled by executing the shell command
</p>

<p>
<code>&nbsp;&nbsp;sudo uninstall-gambc v@VERSION@</code>
</p>

